statements: SELECT * FROM job_market_data;
SELECT job_title, company_name FROM job_market_data WHERE job_location = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM job_market_data ORDER BY job_title ASC;
SELECT job_title, company_name, salary_range FROM job_market_data WHERE skills_required LIKE '%Java%';
SELECT DISTINCT job_location FROM job_market_data;
SELECT * FROM job_market_data WHERE job_location='New York';
SELECT job_title, company_name FROM job_market_data WHERE salary_range='100k-150k';
SELECT job_title, company_name, job_location FROM job_market_data ORDER BY job_title ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS num_jobs FROM job_market_data WHERE skills_required LIKE '%Python%';
SELECT job_title, salary_range FROM job_market_data WHERE company_name='Google' ORDER BY salary_range DESC;
SELECT * FROM JobMarketData;
SELECT job_title, company_name FROM JobMarketData WHERE id = 1;
SELECT id, job_title, skills_required FROM JobMarketData WHERE company_name = 'Tech Corp';
SELECT skill_name, skill_category FROM SkillAnalysis ORDER BY skill_category ASC;
SELECT id, job_title, company_name, skills_required FROM JobMarketData WHERE job_title LIKE '%Engineer%';
SELECT * FROM JobMarketData WHERE job_title = 'Software Engineer';
SELECT id, job_title, company_name FROM JobMarketData WHERE company_name = 'Google';
SELECT skill_name, skill_category FROM SkillAnalysis WHERE skill_level = 'Expert';
SELECT company_name, skills_required FROM JobMarketData WHERE id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT * FROM JobMarketData JOIN SkillAnalysis ON JobMarketData.skills_required = SkillAnalysis.skill_name;
SELECT * FROM job_postings;
SELECT job_title, company_name, job_type FROM job_postings;
SELECT posting_id, job_title, job_description FROM job_postings WHERE job_type='Full-time';
SELECT company_name, job_type, salary_range FROM job_postings ORDER BY job_type DESC;
SELECT posting_id, skill_id FROM skill_requirements WHERE posting_id=101;
SELECT * FROM job_postings;
SELECT job_title, company_name, job_description FROM job_postings WHERE salary_range='High';
SELECT job_title, company_name, job_type FROM job_postings ORDER BY job_type DESC;

SELECT posting_id, job_title, company_name, skill_name FROM job_postings JOIN skill_requirements ON job_postings.posting_id = skill_requirements.posting_id JOIN skills ON skill_requirements.skill_id = skills.skill_id;
SELECT * FROM job_postings WHERE company_name='Tech Co' ORDER BY job_title ASC;
SELECT * FROM job_listings;
SELECT job_title, company_name, location FROM job_listings;
SELECT job_title, salary, job_type FROM job_listings WHERE salary > 50000;
SELECT job_title, company_name, posting_date FROM job_listings ORDER BY posting_date DESC;
SELECT job_title, location, experience_required FROM job_listings WHERE experience_required >= 2;
SELECT job_title, company_name, location, salary FROM job_listings WHERE salary > 50000 ORDER BY posting_date DESC
SELECT job_title, company_name, job_type, experience_required FROM job_listings WHERE experience_required >= 3 ORDER BY job_type ASC
SELECT job_title, job_id FROM job_listings WHERE job_id BETWEEN 100 AND 200 AND location = 'New York'
SELECT company_name, COUNT(job_id) AS job_count FROM job_listings GROUP BY company_name HAVING job_count > 5 ORDER BY job_count DESC
SELECT job_title, skill_name, skill_level FROM job_listings JOIN job_skills ON job_listings.job_id = job_skills.job_id WHERE skill_level = 'Advanced' ORDER BY skill_name
SELECT * FROM jobs;
SELECT job_title, company_name, job_description FROM jobs;

SELECT job_title, skills_required FROM jobs WHERE company_name = 'Example Company';
SELECT job_title, company_name, city, state FROM jobs, job_locations WHERE jobs.job_id = job_locations.location_id;
